\f1\fs30 \cf2 \cb3 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Autism spectrum disorder (ASD) is the name for a group of developmental disorders. ASD includes a wide range, \'93a spectrum,\'94 of symptoms, skills, and levels of disability.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \cb3 Some people are mildly impaired by their symptoms, while others are severely disabled. Treatments and services can improve a person\'92s symptoms and ability to function.\
\
